'''約翰·愛迪律·阿德格波耶加'''（{{lang-en|John Adedayo Adegboyega}}，{{bd|1992年|3月17日}}）或簡稱'''約翰·波耶加'''（{{lang-en|John Boyega}}），是一位英國男演員。出演過較著名的是他在2011年的電影處女作《{{link-en|異星大作戰|Attack the Block}}》<ref>{{cite web |first=Tom |last=Lamont |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/may/08/attack-block-london-teenagers-interview |title=Meet the new kids on the block |publisher=[[The_Observer|The Observer]] |date=2011-05-08 |accessdate=2012-06-24 |archive-date=2011-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111202084350/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/may/08/attack-block-london-teenagers-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而他也於2015年的《[[STAR_WARS：原力覺醒|STAR WARS：原力覺醒]]》起在該系列主演[[芬恩|芬恩]]一角。

==早期生活==
波耶加出生於[[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[佩克漢|佩克漢]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/war-of-the-worlds-meets-skins-on-london-movie-set-2277355.html |title='War of the Worlds' meets 'Skins' on London movie set |first=Andrew |last=McCorkell |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |date=2011-05-01 |publisher=[[Independent_News_&_Media|INM]] |location=London |issn=0951-9467 |oclc=185201487 |accessdate=2012-06-25 |archive-date=2018-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922133357/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/war-of-the-worlds-meets-skins-on-london-movie-set-2277355.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，雙親為奈及利亞人<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/24/movies/john-boyega-in-joe-cornishs-attack-the-block.html?pagewanted=all&_r=1& |title=John Boyega in Joe Cornish’s ‘Attack the Block’ |first=Dave |last=Itzkoff |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2011-07-22 |publisher=[[New_York_Times_Company|NYTC]] |location=[[New_York,_NY|New York]] |issn=0362-4331 |accessdate=2014-12-08 |archive-date=2018-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922133402/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/24/movies/john-boyega-in-joe-cornishs-attack-the-block.html?pagewanted=all&_r=1& |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10多歲時他就讀了{{link-en|威斯敏斯特市學院|Westminster City School}}。後來，他參加了學校的佩卡姆劇院作品的演出。波耶加為[[旺茲沃思|旺茲沃思]]的{{link-en|南泰晤士河學院|South Thames College}}的表演藝術學生，並於2010年參與了全國性的舞台劇《Othello》的演出。

==職業生涯==
波耶加在{{link-en|哈克尼|Metropolitan Borough of Hackney}}的戲劇學院參加訓練<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.identitydramaschool.com/_halloffame.htm |title=Hall of Fame |work=identitydramaschool.com |year=2012 |accessdate=2012-06-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713002415/http://www.identitydramaschool.com/_halloffame.htm |archivedate=2011-07-13 }}</ref>，並於演出電影《{{link-en|異星大作戰|Attack the Block}}》前在[[皇家國立劇場|皇家國立劇場]]和{{link-en|三輪車劇院|Tricycle Theatre}}上分別出演舞台劇《Six Parties》和《Category B》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dvd365.net/featureitem.php?input=attacktheblock |title=Attack the Block feature item |work=dvd365.net |year=2012 |accessdate=2012-06-25 |archive-date=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429202005/http://www.dvd365.net/featureitem.php?input=attacktheblock |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Jen |last=Yamato |url=http://movieline.com/2011/08/01/attack-the-blocks-john-boyega-on-going-from-hoodie-to-hero-and-taking-hollywood-by-storm/ |title=Attack the Block's John Boyega on Going 'From Hoodie to Hero,' and Taking Hollywood by Storm |work=[[Movieline|Movieline]] |date=2011-08-01 |accessdate=2012-06-24 |archive-date=2012-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120711145202/http://movieline.com/2011/08/01/attack-the-blocks-john-boyega-on-going-from-hoodie-to-hero-and-taking-hollywood-by-storm/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2011年9月，[[HBO|HBO]]宣布波耶加將在拳擊劇《Da Brick》的試播集，故事取材於[[麥克·泰森|麥克·泰森]]的一生。描述在[[少年感化院|少年感化院]]中度過18歲生日的唐尼開始找尋自己的定位。該試播集由[[約翰·里德利|約翰·里德利]]負責<ref>{{cite web |first=Catriona |last=Wightman |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/news/a338187/john-boyega-to-star-in-mike-tyson-spike-lee-hbo-pilot-da-brick.html |title=John Boyega to star in Mike Tyson, Spike Lee HBO pilot 'Da Brick' – US TV News |publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |date=2011-09-01 |accessdate=2012-06-24 |archive-date=2012-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120917223138/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/news/a338187/john-boyega-to-star-in-mike-tyson-spike-lee-hbo-pilot-da-brick.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但HBO最後仍沒有讓此劇繼續下去<ref>{{cite web |first=Morgan |last=Jeffery |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/news/a371123/da-brick-hbo-passes-on-mike-tyson-boxing-drama.html |title='Da Brick': HBO passes on Mike Tyson boxing drama – US TV News |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2012-03-14 |accessdate=2012-06-24 |archive-date=2012-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120709054936/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/news/a371123/da-brick-hbo-passes-on-mike-tyson-boxing-drama.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，2011年時，他參演了電影《{{link-en|廢棄的心|Junkhearts}}》，波耶加詮釋一名發現槍枝的毒販，並試圖賣給他人。

2011年7月，波耶加被《{{link-en|Screen International|Screen International}}》雜誌選為「2011年英國明日之星」之一，同時也和另外兩位入選者共同登上該期的封面<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.screendaily.com/festival-calendar/stars-of-tomorrow-2011/5029340.article |title=Stars of Tomorrow 2011 |work=[[Screen_Daily|Screen Daily]] |date=2011-06-30 |accessdate=2014-12-08 |archive-date=2014-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211144012/http://www.screendaily.com/festival-calendar/stars-of-tomorrow-2011/5029340.article |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年3月，宣布波耶加參演了改編自[[奇瑪曼達·恩格茲·阿迪契|奇瑪曼達·恩格茲·阿迪契]]的小說的電影《{{link-en|半輪黃日|Half of a Yellow Sun (film)}}》<ref>{{cite web |first=Ben |last=Pearson |url=http://filmonic.com/attack-the-block-star-john-boyega-joins-half-of-a-yellow-sun/ |title=Attack the Block star John Boyega joins Half of a Yellow Sun |publisher=Filmonic |date=2012-03-29 |accessdate=2012-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160528192012/http://filmonic.com/attack-the-block-star-john-boyega-joins-half-of-a-yellow-sun/ |archive-date=2016-05-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2014年4月29日，證實波耶加他將在《[[STAR_WARS：原力覺醒|STAR WARS：原力覺醒]]》中擔任主要角色，電影於2015年上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://starwars.com/news/star-wars-episode-7-cast-announced.html |title=Star Wars: Episode VII Cast Announced |publisher=StarWars.com |date=2014-04-29 |accessdate=2014-04-29 |archive-date=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429172655/http://starwars.com/news/star-wars-episode-7-cast-announced.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年11月28日，他在接受採訪時，透露粉絲曾支持他飾演[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]的角色[[黑豹_(漫畫)|黑豹]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Get to know 'Star Wars' star John Boyega|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/11/28/showbiz/celebrity-news-gossip/star-wars-who-is-john-boyega|agency=Breeanna Hare, CNN|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2014-11-28|accessdate=2014-12-24|archive-date=2014-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224165551/http://www.cnn.com/2014/11/28/showbiz/celebrity-news-gossip/star-wars-who-is-john-boyega|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但後來此角由[[查德維克·博斯曼|查德維克·博斯曼]]取得。2016年1月，波耶加成立了自己的製片公司Upperroom Entertainment Limited。2016年6月，波耶加證實，他的公司將和[[傳奇影業|傳奇影業]]聯合製作電影《[[環太平洋_(電影)|環太平洋]]》的續集《[[環太平洋2：起義時刻|環太平洋2：起義時刻]]》，而波耶加也將參與演出<ref>{{cite twitter|user=JohnBoyega|number=739865052996620288|title=So happy! My company UpperRoom Productions founded by myself & @MrFemiOguns, will co-produce #PacificRim2 alongside @Legendary|date=2016-06-06}}</ref>。

2016年6月，宣布他將主演[[凱薩琳·畢格羅|凱薩琳·畢格羅]]執導的改編自[[1967年底特律騷亂|1967年底特律騷亂]]電影<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/JohnBoyega/status/745324400078106626 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2016-09-22 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20160922183005/https://twitter.com/JohnBoyega/status/745324400078106626 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歷史驚悚電影《[[底特律_(電影)|底特律]]》於2017年8月上映。

